review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 3, 2020
name: Katherine Turo
title: Wonderful
review: These cultures make a fantastic yogurt! I am extremely satisfied with the end result, rich, creamy and no need to strain for thickness. I let my cultures incubate for 12 full hours, highly recommend letting it gothat long.
